Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, come on! You'd better get out of bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's eight! I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you. Why the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the clock wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a high schooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on starting school here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join the tennis club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Judo Club's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join the Tea Ceremony Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please join the Abacus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.46,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you groaning about, Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Nodoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure which club I should join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You haven't decided on one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been two weeks since school started. You have to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm absolutely terrible at every sport, and I don't really get any of the literary clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how people end up becoming NEETs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pegged as a NEET just 'cause you don't join a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, looking back on it, for as long as I've known you, you've never joined a single club, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Crud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do feel like I ought to at least try to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But what the heck should I be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go check out the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which club do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club! What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was planning on joining the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already filled out the application form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go! Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's disbanded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, on the verge of being disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All the students who were in the club last year have now graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so the club will be disbanded unless four students join this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why there wasn't anyone in the Music Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yamanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Yui. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I have a music class to teach in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Music Club, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure was pretty, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hand out the syllabus sheets to all the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The syllabus sheets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! So sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.08,Default Over,,0,0,0,,She's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being disbanded, so that's that. I'm gonna go join the Literature Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I join and there aren't any members, does that make me the club president?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't sound bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that club you were talking about with those girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club is about playing lighthearted music.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's your plan, Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We wait for prospective members!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I wanted to find out about joining your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm at the Choir Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not join the Light Music Club instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the Choir Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We need more members like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I'm begging you! You won't regret it, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to force her to join like that! It's really rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that promise we made? Was that just a big lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That I would play drums! And then you would play the bass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our band! We've been saying forever that we would start one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised each other, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That night we went to see that concert together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Were those sweet words nothing but a big lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, your flashback is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are going to play in a band together! Is that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You forced the idea on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you said you wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we went pro, we said we'd split all the proceeds 70/30!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be a great deal of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The only instrument I can play is the keyboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like to join your club if you'll have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much! Now we only need one more person to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose that means I'm already a member.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi Kotobuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ritsu Tainaka, drums. This is Mio Akiyama, she's on bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Now we need a guitar player!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My high school years are very important. I wanna do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have absolutely no idea what it is I should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like any french fries with that, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I would love some. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time eating in a fast food restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's silly but I've always dreamed of having someone ask me if I wanted french fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Please begin the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay, this meeting's come to order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to recruit one more member by the end of the month!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're meeting to think of a way right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, offering people an amazing prize if they decide to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,An amazing prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like some kind of gift or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a car or a plane or a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing but impractical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,More along the lines of ice cream or help with homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would join up for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyororin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The president shouldn't lose interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up with something to keep me interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, for now, why don't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... there's just one more week remaining in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's answered our ads yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Disbanded before we are a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Light Music, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, my click, clack, click, clack, here, ha, hi, is a click...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very good at that, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being, I have decided to join the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? So, what is it that they do at this club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But since the name of the club is "light music," I figured they only do really easy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know like whistling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like they don't have much ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? It looks like they're some kind of band.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But I don't know how to play the guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, what can you play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play castanets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, click, fu, clack, fu, click...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a perfect fit for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Look at this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.35,Default Over,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.72,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A prospective member has come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Isn't that wonderful news?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Also that's a lovely tea set, but make sure you clean up after yourselves once you're done, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.50,Default Over,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Now we won't be disbanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui Hirasawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just her name makes her sound really awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got to be a guitarist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! A real powerhouse has joined us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Light music club...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Light music club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get down this hallway, I won't reach the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Light Music Club is up in the Music Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be an easy thing to say right after joining, but I've got to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of people would join a Light Music Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to quit, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could walk away without any consequences?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!\NYou've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's the useless clumsy bad tempo girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Yui Hirasawa by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who wants to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I misjudged you! I'm sure you must be totally awesome on guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all been waiting for you to get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like someone's been embellishing things about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Our brand-new member has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.20,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good to have you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Mugi, go get the tea ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, it's quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should give up on trying to quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind music do you like to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your all time favorite band?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which guitarists do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my... I have to tell them. I can't really play the guitar at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,J... J... J...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say Jimi Hendrix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not. I mean, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jimmy Page, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Oh, no, I ju... ju...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:41.94,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeff Beck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there really this many guitarists whose names start with "J"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, Jeff Beck, that's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the music world, they say that there's only two kind of rock guitarists: Jeff Beck, and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:16:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a brilliant and challenging guitarist who's always searching for new sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so hardcore, Miss Hirasawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta say I'm so glad that someone like her joined the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We were at the point where the club would have been disbanded if we hadn't gotten another member within the next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for joining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep making it harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm... I'm just going to have to spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, I don't know how to say it if I made a mistake joining this club but I only came here to beg you to let me quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't play the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be playing a different kind of instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What instrument can you play, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Casta... Er, the harmonica.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have a harmonica right here. Try playing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Miss Hirasawa, if you wanted to join this club, that means that you're at least interested in music, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there another club you'd rather join?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, none in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let this mark leave this room no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To keep the club from being disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to keep her here somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I really mean it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How about another cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have cookies and madeleines as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.16,Default Over,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're baiting the hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So good... I-I'm sorry, I didn't mean to come here and gorge myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should start eating snacks like this every day from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we drifting off topic here... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hirasawa, what other sorts of things do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I like anything that tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, just food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,On your days off, do you spend your time at home doing anything in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sitting around, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I like cute things, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very good with extreme heat or cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I spend winter under the table where it's warm. And in the summer, I spend my time on the floor where it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't go, I'm begging you! You can just hang out and do nothing if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to bring even tastier snacks, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't take things seriously when I applied to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I got all your hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I ever apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the ones who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't have tried to force you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So please! At least hang around for a while and listen to us play a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll play a song for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's swallowed the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard to put into words!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't very good, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about blunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seemed like it would be a whole lot of fun to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that I'm going to join this club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's commemorate the start of the Light Music Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But the problem is that I can't play any instruments at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I be a manager or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we aren't a sports club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, why don't you take this opportunity to begin learning the guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks very complicated! I don't think I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Between the three of us, we'll teach you everything you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to you play just now made me feel like I can do at least that well, if not a lot better!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So glad to be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You went ahead and joined anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They practically begged me to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, as a manager or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When someone else says it, it sounds insulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I joined as a full-fledged member of the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say they'll teach me to play guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that means you're gonna have to go out and buy yourself a new guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll let me borrow one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy them for about $50, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy. I wonder if the Light Music Club knows what they're getting themselves into with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone! These three are my fellow Light Music Club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to pick a club where I could make friends with sort of fun, pleasant people that one so rarely meets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I finally made it to high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've joined a club for the first time!
